body.p: The following Norsemen bought or sold real estate in Chicago during the past week:
John M. Carlson to John O. Lochner: Kenilworth Avenue, west of Robey Street. Price, $5,000.
P. M. Christiansen to Charles T.Christiansen: North 44th Court, north of Cortland Street. Price, $3,600.
F. Schmidtz to Hans E. Hagglund: 360-562 Orleans Street. Price, $2,050. Price, $2,050.
J. J. Rumpf to Simon Nelson: Humboldt Boulevard, north of Cortland Street. Price, $1,500.
M. R. Bortsee to Frank Lindquist: 51st Court, corner of Indiana Avenue.Court, corner of Indiana Avenue.
J. E. De Lacy to Samuel Olsen: Turner Avenue, south of 21st Street. Price, $3,000.
C. A. McDonald to J. M. Johnson: Fulton Street, east of Lincoln Street. Price, $2,900.
C. Iversen to W. F. Temptel: Austin, Johnston Addition, lot 1, block 12. Price, $6,500.
